2011-09-08T07:04:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-09-08/china-glaze-co-august-sales-rise-14-72-table-1809-tt.html
CHINA GLAZE CO said unconsolidated sales
in August rose 14.72% to NT$147,243,000 from NT$128,345,000,
according to a statement filed to the Taiwan Stock Exchange.  (Figures are in thousands of New Taiwan dollars)  =================================================================  8/2011           8/2010
Sales            147,243          128,345    
YOY%              14.72%   -----------------Year-to-date-----------------
Sales           1,063,231         999,544    
YOY%              6.37%  
=================================================================
 